TITLE: Episode 46 - Down With the Sickness
DESCRIPTION: Jessie and Maddie talk about being sick of Covid and how it just made 2020 and people, in general, more annoying. There is mention of a certain dead president who might have created AIDS in a Canadian bio-weapons lab and discussion of the new normal.
